functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: What are the names of the cities used for the latest 4 macOS versions and their geographic coordinates?
What are the names of the cities used for the latest 4 macOS versions and their geographic coordinates?

The latest four macOS versions and their corresponding city names with geographic coordinates are:

1. macOS Sonoma (2024): The name is inspired by Sonoma County in California, USA, located at approximately 38.2963° N, 122.5373° W.

2. macOS Ventura (2022): Named after Ventura, a city in California, USA, situated at approximately 34.2739° N, 119.2415° W.

3. macOS Monterey (2021): Derived from Monterey, California, USA, with coordinates around 36.6007° N, 121.8946° W.

4. macOS Big Sur (2020): Refers to the Big Sur region in California, USA, which stretches along the coast with coordinates varying, but approximately 36.2297° N, 121.7611° W for the Big Sur River Inlet.
